      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Games\" title=\"Games\">Games</a> * Chinese Dark Chess</b>\n</p><p><b>Chinese Dark Chess</b> (暗棋),<br />\na popular version of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Banqi\">Banqi</a>, a variation of <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Chinese Chess</a> that only uses half of the board, also called <i>dark chess</i>, <i>half chess</i> or <i>blind chess</i>. Chinese dark chess is a <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Two-player_game\">two-player</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zero-sum_%28game_theory%29\">zero-sum</a> and incomplete information <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Board_game\">board game</a>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Photos\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Tournaments\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournaments</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Photos\">Photos</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chinese_Dark_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Photos\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"floatnone\"><a href=\"https://icga.org/?page_id=849&amp;wppa-album=6&amp;wppa-cover=0&amp;wppa-occur=1&amp;wppa-photo=83\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"DarkChess2013.jpg\" src=\"/images/a/ab/DarkChess2013.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"424\" style=\"vertical-align: text-bottom\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></div> \n<p><a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">Yokohama 2013</a> award ceremony <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Chinese Dark Chess</a>, <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a> (Operator Yahari, Bronze),<br /><a href=\"/Wen-Jie_Tseng\" title=\"Wen-Jie Tseng\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (DarkKnight, Gold), <a href=\"/Cheng-Wei_Chou\" title=\"Cheng-Wei Chou\">Cheng-Wei Chou</a> (Diablo, Silver), and <a href=\"/Jaap_van_den_Herik\" title=\"Jaap van den Herik\">Jaap van den Herik</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> \n|}\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournaments\">Tournaments</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chinese_Dark_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Tournaments\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<