Wen-Jie_Tseng\" title=\"Wen-Jie Tseng\">Wen-Jie Tseng</a> (<b>2013</b>).  <i>DARKNIGHT Wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#36_3\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 36, No. 3</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/17th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"17th Computer Olympiad\">17th Computer Olympiad</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Shi-Jim_Yen\" title=\"Shi-Jim Yen\">Shi-Jim Yen</a>, <a href=\"/Cheng-Wei_Chou\" title=\"Cheng-Wei Chou\">Cheng-Wei Chou</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Kuo-Yuan_Kao\" title=\"Kuo-Yuan Kao\">Kuo-Yuan Kao</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Design and Implementation of Chinese Dark Chess Programs</i>. Computational Intelligence and AI in Games</li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicolas_Jouandeau&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nicolas Jouandeau (page does not exist)\">Nicolas Jouandeau</a>, <a href=\"/Tristan_Cazenave\" title=\"Tristan Cazenave\">Tristan Cazenave</a> (<b>2014</b>). <i>Small and Large MCTS Playouts applied to Chinese Dark Chess Stochastic Game</i>. <a href=\"/index.php?title=ECAI_CGW_2014&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ECAI CGW 2014 (page does not exist)\">ECAI CGW 2014</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Chinese_Dark_Chess&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Chu-Hsuan_Hsueh\" title=\"Chu-Hsuan Hsueh\">Chu-Hsuan Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a> (<b>2015</b>). <i>DARKKNIGHT wins Chinese Dark Chess Tournament</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#38_4\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 38, No. 4</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/18th_Computer_Olympiad#ChineseDarkChess\" title=\"