_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gang-Yu Fan (page does not exist)\">Gang-Yu Fan</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Chih-Wen_Hsueh\" title=\"Chih-Wen Hsueh\">Chih-Wen Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-319-75931-9_10\">Validating and Fine-Tuning of Game Evaluation Functions Using Endgame Databases</a></i>. <a href=\"/Conferences#IJCAI2017\" title=\"Conferences\">CGW@IJCAI 2017</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Gang-Yu_Fan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Gang-Yu Fan (page does not exist)\">Gang-Yu Fan</a>, <a href=\"/Chih-Wen_Hsueh\" title=\"Chih-Wen Hsueh\">Chih-Wen Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>  (<b>2018</b>). <i>Using Chinese dark chess endgame databases to validate and fine-tune game evaluation functions</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 2</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Endgame_Tablebases\" title=\"Endgame Tablebases\">Endgame Tablebases</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Chih-Wen_Hsueh\" title=\"Chih-Wen Hsueh\">Chih-Wen Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2018</b>). <i>Analysis and efficient solutions for 2 × 4 Chinese dark chess</i>. <a href=\"/ICGA_Journal#40_2\" title=\"ICGA Journal\">ICGA Journal, Vol. 40, No. 2</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Chu-Hsuan_Hsueh\" title=\"Chu-Hsuan Hsueh\">Chu-Hsuan Hsueh</a>, <a href=\"/I-Chen_Wu\" title=\"I-Chen Wu\">I-Chen Wu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-